short_description: star engineers india private limited is an electronical components manufacturer based in pimpri-chinchwad, india.
long_description: at star, we specialize in designing, developing, manufacturing, and supplying a diverse range of automotive and non-automotive electronic components to global oems in various applications. our product offerings include ignition controls, sensors, regulators and rectifiers, flashers, chargers, converters, and electronic throttles, catering to both automotive and non-automotive segments. our in-house r&d team of experts, backed by global technology partners, enables us to create cutting-edge technology products that meet the evolving needs of our customers. as a global leader in electronic component manufacturing, we take pride in our world-class research and development facilities that ensure we remain at the forefront of innovation in our industry. we believe in developing long-term partnerships with our customers and strive to offer the best value proposition in terms of cost, quality, delivery, and customer service. to cater to our global customers, star has established state-of-the-art facilities for designing and manufacturing in india and vietnam. equipped with ultra-modern resources, including cutting-edge emission testing and endurance testing facilities, we are able to design and validate product performance with unparalleled precision. our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction has enabled us to emerge as a world-class supplier of electronic components. we will continue to leverage our technical expertise, state-of-the-art facilities, and global partnerships to meet the evolving needs of our customers and remain at the forefront of innovation in our industry. we believe that innovation is the key to success in the highly competitive electronic components industry. our brand philosophy centers around the principles of quality, innovation, and customer service.
